edu.pdx.cs410J.kathtran

Class PhoneBill

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.pdx.cs410J.AbstractPhoneBill
      • edu.pdx.cs410J.kathtran.PhoneBill
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PhoneBill
extends AbstractPhoneBill
    Implements the abstract methods that can be found within the AbstractPhoneBill in addition to new methods that support the construction of the phone bill skeleton. The customer's name as well as their collection of phone call records are maintained here.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kathleen Tran
    See Also:
